briefTitle: Fujifilm Feature Comparison Reader Study to Compare Old vs New Processing
officialTitle: A Feature Comparison Study to Evaluate the Modified Processing of Fujifilm's ASPIRE Cristalle With Digital Breast Tomosynthesis Option as Compared to the Original Processing
primaryOutcomeMeasure: Comparison of ISR (Modified Processing) to FBP (Original Processing)
eligibilityCriteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* Female subjects participating in FMSU2013-004A protocol with known clinical status

Exclusion Criteria:

* Female subjects that did not have known clinical status in FMSU2013-004A
